TextEng: Wow! You really don't like Damas.
You're pretty hard on your Commander. He's just doing his job.
Text: 사령관에게 너무 가혹하네. 그냥 일하는 거잖아.

TextEng: Do you want me to try and speak to Damas on your behalf?
I'll be going now.
Anything I can do to help?
Text: 내가 도울 수 있는 게 있어?

TextEng: Like you said, we gnomes have to stick together. Is there anything I can do to help?
Text: 네 말대로, 우리 노움들끼리는 뭉쳐야지. 내가 도울 수 있는 게 있을까?

TextEng: You not like Damas much.
Damas be commander. He just do job.
Want me speak at Damas?
Me go now.
Me want help you.
You gnome like me. Me help you.
Text: 너 나처럼 노움이야. 나 너 도울게.

TextEng: Okay, I'll do it.
What's in this for me?
I've got more important things to worry about.
Me do it!
What me get if me do it?
Me not got time for this.
Me look for Power Words. You know where they be?
Text: 나 권능의 언령 찾아. 너 어디 있는지 알아?

TextEng: You wouldn't know anything about some ancient artifacts know as the Words of Power, would you?
Text: 권능의 언령이라는 고대 유물에 대해 아는 게 있어?
